1
00:00:23,000 --> 00:00:24,730
Sun Wen, I've been busy lately.

2
00:00:24,760 --> 00:00:27,090
I'll contact you when things settle down.

3
00:01:42,640 --> 00:01:44,200
How is Xixi?

4
00:01:46,200 --> 00:01:48,060
You're finally willing to see me.

5
00:01:49,600 --> 00:01:50,640
You lied to me.

6
00:01:51,000 --> 00:01:51,759
Sit.

7
00:01:55,560 --> 00:01:57,080
You seem very busy lately.

8
00:01:59,400 --> 00:02:00,200
Don't worry.

9
00:02:00,920 --> 00:02:02,560
Qiu Shili watched cartoons with Xixi

10
00:02:02,560 --> 00:02:03,920
and put her to sleep.

11
00:02:06,200 --> 00:02:07,160
I'll pour you some water.

12
00:02:07,160 --> 00:02:07,800
Thanks.

13
00:02:09,080 --> 00:02:10,840
But I might need to trouble you guys

14
00:02:10,840 --> 00:02:12,920
to take care of Xixi for a while longer.

15
00:02:12,920 --> 00:02:14,480
I've asked Chen Jian for a divorce.

16
00:02:14,480 --> 00:02:15,480
The house is sold.

17
00:02:15,840 --> 00:02:18,240
I'll be staying in a hotel. It's safe.

18
00:02:19,280 --> 00:02:20,960
If things go smoothly,

19
00:02:21,960 --> 00:02:23,840
I can bring Xixi home soon.

20
00:02:26,800 --> 00:02:27,600
Thank you.

21
00:02:32,560 --> 00:02:34,290
What if it doesn't go smoothly?

22
00:02:36,160 --> 00:02:37,400
What did you say?

23
00:02:37,960 --> 00:02:38,800
I said, if it doesn't go smoothly,

24
00:02:38,800 --> 00:02:41,160
do we have to raise Xixi for you?

25
00:02:42,640 --> 00:02:44,640
You pushed my lantern into the water

26
00:02:44,760 --> 00:02:47,120
to stop me from contacting you twelve days later.

27
00:02:47,120 --> 00:02:48,560
And you deliberately rushed to change the plan

28
00:02:48,560 --> 00:02:50,090
to make Chen Jian leave you.

29
00:02:51,240 --> 00:02:53,040
Something happens twelve days later, right?

30
00:02:53,040 --> 00:02:54,800
No, it's not that.

31
00:02:54,960 --> 00:02:55,760
The lantern,

32
00:02:55,800 --> 00:02:57,079
fell into the water by accident.

33
00:02:57,079 --> 00:02:58,960
I saw it. It wasn't an accident.

34
00:03:08,800 --> 00:03:09,440
Sun Wen.

35
00:03:10,800 --> 00:03:11,520
Trust me.

36
00:03:11,880 --> 00:03:13,400
I have the ability to solve this myself.

37
00:03:13,400 --> 00:03:14,600
How will you solve it?

38
00:03:15,040 --> 00:03:16,040
What if you don't?

39
00:03:16,040 --> 00:03:16,720
Tell me.

40
00:03:16,720 --> 00:03:17,920
There is no "what if".

41
00:03:18,760 --> 00:03:19,690
Even if there is,

42
00:03:20,200 --> 00:03:21,480
I don't want to involve you anymore.

43
00:03:21,480 --> 00:03:22,720
I can't drag you down.

44
00:03:28,680 --> 00:03:30,340
Do you know what you just said?

45
00:03:31,240 --> 00:03:33,800
If you don't want to drag me down, don't pull me in.

46
00:03:33,800 --> 00:03:35,860
Do you expect me to just watch you die?

47
00:03:36,560 --> 00:03:38,440
What are you two arguing about in the middle of the night?

48
00:03:38,440 --> 00:03:39,160
Go back.

49
00:03:39,480 --> 00:03:40,040
Alright.

50
00:03:41,760 --> 00:03:42,560
Sun Wen.

51
00:03:43,280 --> 00:03:44,760
I already owe you too much.

52
00:03:44,760 --> 00:03:46,440
Then you should live well.

53
00:03:46,440 --> 00:03:47,640
You need to cherish your life,

54
00:03:47,640 --> 00:03:49,440
instead of risking it all alone.

55
00:03:50,760 --> 00:03:51,960
You asked me back then

56
00:03:52,720 --> 00:03:54,980
if I'd regret the price of changing fate.

57
00:03:57,079 --> 00:03:58,079
I don't regret it.

58
00:03:58,520 --> 00:04:00,760
I can tell you,

59
00:04:01,040 --> 00:04:02,760
that I still don't regret it either.

60
00:04:02,760 --> 00:04:03,680
But please,

61
00:04:03,680 --> 00:04:05,080
don't think you can go

62
00:04:05,440 --> 00:04:07,170
and solve every problem alone.

63
00:04:08,360 --> 00:04:10,120
I know how people are.

64
00:04:10,360 --> 00:04:11,890
Before seeing the outcome,

65
00:04:12,080 --> 00:04:14,280
they often act on pure impulse,

66
00:04:14,440 --> 00:04:16,000
regardless of the cost, right or wrong.

67
00:04:16,000 --> 00:04:17,000
But you're different.

68
00:04:17,000 --> 00:04:19,000
You have Xixi. You must think of her.

69
00:04:19,320 --> 00:04:20,640
You, me, and Qiu Shili...

70
00:04:20,640 --> 00:04:22,520
We did everything we could to save Xixi.

71
00:04:22,520 --> 00:04:23,840
Fine. If you tell me now

72
00:04:24,040 --> 00:04:25,200
that we can ignore Xixi,

73
00:04:25,200 --> 00:04:25,960
then no problem.

74
00:04:25,960 --> 00:04:27,680
But if something happens later,

75
00:04:27,680 --> 00:04:29,540
can we just stop caring about her?

76
00:04:29,640 --> 00:04:30,440
No.

77
00:04:31,640 --> 00:04:32,440
Are you looking for me?

78
00:04:32,440 --> 00:04:33,320
Shut up.

79
00:04:33,680 --> 00:04:34,680
Okay.

80
00:04:43,200 --> 00:04:44,000
Okay.

81
00:04:45,560 --> 00:04:46,360
Okay.

82
00:04:48,920 --> 00:04:49,960
I understand.

83
00:05:09,760 --> 00:05:10,760
Security!

84
00:05:10,760 --> 00:05:11,480
There's someone in my room.

85
00:05:11,480 --> 00:05:13,940
There's someone in my room. In the bathroom.

86
00:05:25,200 --> 00:05:26,600
I'm sorry, Ms. Wen.

87
00:05:26,600 --> 00:05:28,360
Mr. Chen had his ID and marriage certificate,

88
00:05:28,360 --> 00:05:29,680
so we let him in.

89
00:05:32,600 --> 00:05:34,159
Okay, thanks.

90
00:06:10,000 --> 00:06:10,800
Sun Wen.

91
00:06:11,280 --> 00:06:12,400
Chen Jian took my revolving lantern

92
00:06:12,400 --> 00:06:13,640
and my diary.

93
00:06:21,160 --> 00:06:21,960
Jianjian.

94
00:06:24,000 --> 00:06:25,530
Are we really leaving here?

95
00:06:27,280 --> 00:06:28,080
Mom.

96
00:06:28,640 --> 00:06:31,840
You go first tomorrow. I still have some things to handle.

97
00:06:31,960 --> 00:06:34,080
I'll go with you after you're done.

98
00:06:35,920 --> 00:06:37,159
I want to be with you.

99
00:06:38,680 --> 00:06:39,480
Mom.

100
00:06:42,400 --> 00:06:45,460
Jianjian, if your wife is gone, we can find another one.

101
00:06:45,880 --> 00:06:48,159
If the child is gone, you can have another one.

102
00:06:48,159 --> 00:06:50,280
It was a daughter, not a son, anyway.

103
00:06:51,480 --> 00:06:54,480
I still have some savings. Let's go back to our hometown.

104
00:06:54,480 --> 00:06:57,440
If you want to do business, I'll do it with you.

105
00:06:58,159 --> 00:07:00,480
Whatever you want to do, I'll be with you.

106
00:07:00,480 --> 00:07:01,600
It's okay.

107
00:07:33,280 --> 00:07:34,740
Why aren't you asleep yet?

108
00:07:35,200 --> 00:07:36,400
I'm working on something.

109
00:07:36,400 --> 00:07:38,200
You go to sleep first. I'll be there in a bit.

110
00:07:38,200 --> 00:07:39,530
What are you working on?

111
00:07:39,800 --> 00:07:41,159
The revolving lantern you invented last time

112
00:07:41,159 --> 00:07:42,200
only sold one unit.

113
00:07:42,200 --> 00:07:43,400
If you invent anything else,

114
00:07:43,400 --> 00:07:45,659
our warehouse won't be able to fit it all.

115
00:07:45,920 --> 00:07:46,760
Go. Go away.

116
00:07:47,440 --> 00:07:48,159
Go away.

117
00:07:48,400 --> 00:07:49,400
I was just joking.

118
00:07:49,840 --> 00:07:51,970
But your bed is really uncomfortable.

119
00:07:53,440 --> 00:07:55,560
It's really cramped for my long legs.

120
00:07:57,640 --> 00:07:58,920
Sorry, sorry.

121
00:08:00,600 --> 00:08:02,660
If you don't like my bed, that's fine.

122
00:08:03,000 --> 00:08:05,200
You can use those long legs of yours

123
00:08:05,200 --> 00:08:08,600
to walk back to your own house to sleep. It's faster.

124
00:08:09,480 --> 00:08:10,080
Fine.

125
00:08:10,240 --> 00:08:12,240
Bye-bye. See you.

126
00:08:12,360 --> 00:08:14,440
But Xixi needs me. Don't you, Xixi?

127
00:08:17,240 --> 00:08:18,920
You clap one.

128
00:08:18,920 --> 00:08:20,120
I clap one.

129
00:08:20,360 --> 00:08:23,040
A little kid on a plane.

130
00:08:23,880 --> 00:08:26,200
Handsome, could you help me out?

131
00:08:26,800 --> 00:08:27,480
Xixi,

132
00:08:27,880 --> 00:08:28,920
wait for me here for a second, okay?

133
00:08:28,920 --> 00:08:29,680
Okay.

134
00:08:30,600 --> 00:08:31,280
Of course.

135
00:08:31,720 --> 00:08:32,559
My pleasure.

136
00:08:33,760 --> 00:08:34,559
What's wrong?

137
00:08:35,280 --> 00:08:37,760
Could you help by adding me on WeChat?

138
00:08:38,600 --> 00:08:40,480
That's not really appropriate.

139
00:08:45,640 --> 00:08:46,400
All done.

140
00:08:48,960 --> 00:08:49,760
Xixi!

141
00:08:51,160 --> 00:08:52,000
Xixi!

142
00:08:52,760 --> 00:08:53,560
Xixi!

143
00:08:56,120 --> 00:08:56,920
Xixi!
